X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/2007/4/20/158

This function were placed in "#if 0" because nobody was using it.
We using it now.
See 
http://lwn.net/Articles/210610/
Signed-off-by: Anton Vorontsov <cbou@mail.ru>
